2003-07-19 06:57  bellardo

	* firebird2/builds/posix/: Makefile.in.boot.gpre,
	Makefile.in.codes, Makefile.in.embed.lockmgr, Makefile.in.fbserver,
	Makefile.in.inet_server, Makefile.in.static.gbak,
	Makefile.in.static.gpre, make.shared.targets, prefix.darwin:
	
	Darwin can't handle -L<space>lib_include_dir parameter to linker,
	so all instances have been changed to -Llib_include_dir.  Also
	update the darwin platform prefix file.

