2003-04-06 13:40  alexpeshkoff

	* firebird2/src/: jrd/svc.cpp, jrd/gds.cpp, jrd/gds_proto.h,
	jrd/isc.cpp, jrd/isc_proto.h, qli/help.epp, gpre/ftn.cpp:
	
