2003-02-09 03:07  arnobrinkman

	* firebird2/src/jrd/cmp.cpp:
	
	bugfix: SF BUG # [ 523589 ] View is affecting the result of a
	query. Problem was that rse's (inside the view) where not flagged
	as variant

